Reign of Grelok

This is a small adventure game written in Ruby. You play as Grognak, a mighty barbarian, and your goal is to put an end to the terrible reign of Grelok, an evil wizard.

The story originates from Fallout 3 minigame Reign of Grelok (beta): http://fallout.wikia.com/wiki/Reign_of_Grelok_(beta)

Commands:
- movement: n(orth), s(outh), e(ast), w(est)
- inventory: i(nventory)
- look at thing: e(xamine), l(ook at)
- pick up thing: t(ake), p(ick up)
- drop thing: d(rop)

- general use of items: use [thing] (on) [thing|npc|monster]
- communication with npcs: talk to (tt), ask [npc] (about) [thing]
- fight: attack [monster] (with) [thing], use [thing] (on) [monster]
